OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly patches of low cloud and
OL,6,Ffog will readily clear during the
OL,7,Fmorning to leave a dry day across the
OL,8,Fcountry with plenty of sunny spells,
OL,9,Fmost prolonged in the southwest.
OL,10,FFeeling very warm in the light
OL,11,Fnorthwesterly winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will remain dry overnight
OL,14,Fwith variable cloud. There will be
OL,15,Fsome clear spells, though patches of
OL,16,Flow cloud and fog are likely to reform
OL,17,Fby the morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
