OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FFriday looks set to be another
OL,6,Ffine day. The morning may start a bit
OL,7,Fgrey and misty for some, but plenty of
OL,8,Fsunshine will develop, heralding a
OL,9,Fvery warm afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FFurther
OL,12,Fwarm sunshine on Saturday. Conditions
OL,13,Fturning more changeable later, and
OL,14,Finto Sunday, with some showery and
OL,15,Fbreezy weather moving through from the
OL,16,Fnorthwest. Perhaps a few showers on
OL,17,FMonday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
